<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Sources & Attribution</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Arabic Qurʾān Text</h2>
      
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Source Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The Arabic Qurʾān text used in this application is sourced from the Tanzil Project, 
          specifically the Ḥafṣ ʿan ʿĀṣim recitation in Uthmānī script.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">Attribution Details:</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Source:</strong> Tanzil Uthmani</li>
            <li><strong>Publisher:</strong> Tanzil Project</li>
            <li><strong>License:</strong> CC BY 3.0</li>
            <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://tanzil.net/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">https://tanzil.net/</a></li>
            <li><strong>Recitation:</strong> Ḥafṣ ʿan ʿĀṣim</li>
            <li><strong>Script:</strong> Uthmānī (globally standard orthography)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Data Integrity</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          All Arabic text is stored with SHA-256 checksums to ensure data integrity. 
          The original source files are preserved without modification.
        </p>
        
        <% if SourceRegistry.exists? %>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-800 mb-2">Current Source Registry:</h4>
            <% SourceRegistry.all.each do |source| %>
              <div class="text-sm text-blue-700 mb-2">
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= source.name %></p>
                <p><strong>Version:</strong> <%= source.version %></p>
                <p><strong>Checksum:</strong> <code class="bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded"><%= source.checksum_sha256 %></code></p>
                <% if source.notes.present? %>
                  <p><strong>Notes:</strong> <%= source.notes %></p>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Usage Rights</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          This application uses the Arabic Qurʾān text under the Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 license. 
          The text is used without modification and proper attribution is provided.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h4 class="font-medium text-green-800 mb-2">License Compliance:</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-green-700 space-y-1">
            <li>✅ Original text preserved without modification</li>
            <li>✅ Proper attribution provided</li>
            <li>✅ Source checksums maintained for verification</li>
            <li>✅ License information clearly displayed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Data Statistics</h2>
      
      <% if TextUnit.exists? %>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">Import Statistics</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li><strong>Total Verses:</strong> <%= TextUnit.count %></li>
              <li><strong>Total Surahs:</strong> <%= TextUnit.distinct.count(:chapter) %></li>
              <li><strong>Text Payloads:</strong> <%= TextPayload.count %></li>
              <li><strong>Canon Mappings:</strong> <%= CanonMap.count %></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">Coverage</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <% surahs = TextUnit.distinct.pluck(:chapter).sort %>
              <li><strong>Surahs Covered:</strong> <%= surahs.join(', ') %></li>
              <li><strong>Language:</strong> Arabic (ara)</li>
              <li><strong>Script:</strong> Arabic (Arab)</li>
              <li><strong>Edition:</strong> Quran_Hafs_Uthmani_Tanzil</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No Quran data has been imported yet.</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        For questions about data sources or to report issues, please 
        <a href="<%= contact_path %>" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
